Rep.<b> Greg</b>] <b>Steube</b> pitching, and [Missouri Sen. <b>Eric</b>]<b=
> Schmitt</b> hitting, are probably your stars. Apparently a late injury to=
 [Michigan Rep.<b> Bill</b>]<b> Huizenga</b> will cause some movement in th=
e infield.=E2=80=9D <br/><br/>The coach on the Democratic side, California =
Rep. <b>Linda</b> <b>S=C3=A1nchez</b>, is feeling confident. =E2=80=9CLast =
year, we had a young team with lots of freshman players,=E2=80=9D she told =
